column5: Have a great day all...for some it's a holiday, for others the week is half over     Either way... enjoy   :blahblah1:  Maureen
And for some of us, every day is a holiday......Mornin Moe

Top of the Morning to Ya. Yeppers....it's FRIDAY for me!!  Itching to get some fishing in - heading to Petrie Island with my 13 yr old son over the next few days.  Hope to have a report with loads of pics  lol  Happy Summer Everyone
Good morning Mo... the weeks half over for me... but a longgggg day ahead today...  Have a good one....
An hour an 15 to quittin time, looks like a little bit of rain on the horizon.  Hump day or  half way through the week, off to the trailer this morning, pitter patter on the tin roof.
Good luck and have fun!  And hey, besides Fisherman and myself who are currently at work and have a good excuse to be up so early, I've got to ask the rest of you: don't you ever sleep?
Why would anyone want to sleep past 3:00 AM Mike, it's the best part of the day
Morn,n,sure hope it rains like it looks like it will.Mighty dry up here.  Lew Im getting close to yer wake ups.Im at 4 am right now,just need a coffe or two to get the blood goin.LOL
